      "comment": "OH BONNIE (1) out of the placings last few but draws down on the inside. Last time finished last in a Grade 6 on June 15 over 515m at Launceston behind Zipping Randle beaten 73 lengths (35.00). Has claims if she runs up to expectations. TAPA SULLY (3) copped a check in the run and finished a well held 9 lengths third (20.40) last time in a Grade 6 at this track over 340m. Harder here but will be in this for a long way. BLACKBRUSH BILL (2) has shown good improvement at his last two starts, hitting the frame latest when 2nd at this track over 340m. Expected to feature. ZEUS DANGER (8) is new to this trip but cannot be left out.",
